          </listitem>
          <listitem>
            <para>
              Click the <guibutton>Yes</guibutton> button to display the Java EE perspective.
            </para>
            <formalpara><title>Result:</title>
            <para>
              The project is configured and the Java EE perspective is displayed.
            </para>
          </formalpara>
